  sender: Human Resources
  subject: Well Done
  message: "Hey there,\r\n\r\nWe heard you've done such a swell job helping our clients.
    The higher-ups said we should level up your tasks. You can now check your archive\u2014two
    new additions have been added\u2014and, lastly, a dispatch button allowing you
    to send help for clients dealing with high-risk-level entities. Keep in mind,
    you still need to read the solutions in the archive. And don't worry, the pay
    will match.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nI.E.R.F. Human Resources\r\n"
